      "content": "hey, i need help with a trip to tokyo next week. im going to be mostly in shibuya and marunouchi for meetings. can u help me put together a rough itinerary for a monday? i need to know how long it takes to get between those two areas and if u can suggest some quiet cafes in either spot where i can actually get some work done.",
