      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good, thanks. A 10 minute taxi seems pretty quick though, is traffic usually okay on a monday morning? Also, can u give me a more specific breakdown of the transit? Like the train lines i should look for if i decided to take the subway instead of a taxi? Shibuya can get pretty overwhelming with the crowds so i just want to be prepared for the layout.",
